# EXPERIMENT 1: FORMATION OF YBUS AND ZBUS MATRIX

```matlab
clc;
clear all;
close all;

n=input('Enter number of buses: ');

Y=zeros(n,n);

for i=1:n
    for j=1:n
        if(i==j)
            Y(i,j)=3;
        else
            Y(i,j)=-1;
        end
    end
end

Z=inv(Y);

disp('YBUS Matrix');
disp(Y);

disp('ZBUS Matrix');
disp(Z);

disp('Program Executed Successfully');
```

