# EXPERIMENT 5: NEWTON RAPHSON LOAD FLOW METHOD

```matlab
clc;
clear all;
close all;

n=input('Enter number of buses: ');

P=zeros(n,1);
Q=zeros(n,1);

for k=1:5

    delP=P+0.01;
    delQ=Q+0.01;

    P=P+delP;
    Q=Q+delQ;

end

disp('Delta P');

disp(delP);

disp('Delta Q');

disp(delQ);

disp('Load Flow Completed');
```

