# EXPERIMENT 9: TRANSIENT STABILITY ANALYSIS

```matlab
clc;
clear all;
close all;

t=0:0.05:1;

Pm=1;

Pe=0.6;

Pa=Pm-Pe;

delta=45+Pa*50*t;

plot(t,delta);

xlabel('Time (sec)');

ylabel('Rotor Angle (degree)');

title('Swing Curve');

grid on;

disp('Transient Stability Analysis Completed');
```

